{"lemma":"عُمَرِيّ","slug":"عُمَرِيّ","root":"ع.م.ر","root_slug":"ع-م-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-م-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":0},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30523","n30524"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8F%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30523","headword_ar":"عُمْرَى","root":"Emr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a subst., ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_isomN","text_ar":"اـِسْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[strangely read by Golius"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asomaru","text_ar":"اَسْمَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], S, O,) or an inf. n., (TA,) [or rather a quasiinf. n.,] from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEomarahu daArFA","text_ar":"اَعْمَرَهُ دَارًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the like; (S, O, TA;) A man's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assigning to another a house for the life of the latter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the life of the former;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(accord. to the explanation of the verb in the K;) a man's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saying to another, of a house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of camels, It is thine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they are thine, for my life,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for thy life, and when thou diest it returns,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they return, to me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(accord. to the explanation of the verb in the S and Mgh and O;) a man's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"giving to another a house, and saying to him, This is thine for thy life,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for my life:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Th, in TA: [in which is added, “ whichever of us dies, ”"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ay~nA mAt","text_ar":"ايّنا مات"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this I consider a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*aA maAta","text_ar":"اـِذَا مَاتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", “ when he dies, ”) “ the house is given to his family: ”]) so they used to do in the Time of Ignorance: (TA:) but some of the Muslim lawyers hold the gift to be absolute, and the condition to be null. (TA, &c.) ―         -b2-  Also [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so given;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is assigned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"given, to another for the period of his life,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for that of the life of the giver."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruqobaY","text_ar":"رُقْبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["TA"]},{"entry_id":"n30524","headword_ar":"عُمْرِىٌّ","root":"Emr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", applied to trees ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ajar","text_ar":"شَجَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Old;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) a rel. n. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EumorN","text_ar":"عُمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eumoriy~apN","text_ar":"عُمْرِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [the fem.,] applied to a tree ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ajarap","text_ar":"شَجَرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"), signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"great and old, having had a long life:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, TA:) or the former, the [species of lote-tree called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sidor","text_ar":"سِدْر"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that grows upon the rivers"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and imbibes the water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuboriY~N","text_ar":"عُبْرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O:) or, accord, to Abu-l-'Ameythel [or 'Omeythil] El-Aarábee, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"old,"},{"kind":"text","text":"whether on a river or not; (O, TA;) and in like manner says As, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"old"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sidor","text_ar":"سِدْر"},{"kind":"text","text":", whether on a river or not; and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAl","text_ar":"ضَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the recent thereof: some say that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a substitute for the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuboriY~N","text_ar":"عُبْرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","IAth","O","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%B9%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%8A/","headword_ar":"عمري","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23428#f21888","body_html":"<span>العمري: هبة شيء مدة عمر الموهوب له، أو الواهب بشرط الاسترداد بعد موت الموهوب له. مثل أن يقول: داري لك عمري، فتمليكه صحيح وشرطه باطل.</span>"}]}}